templates.name: Search phrase 7
templates.text: Profile: ESSITY HIGIENE Y SALUD MEXICO S A
templates.cypher: MATCH r1 = (n)-[r]-(m) WHERE ID(n) = 922785 AND NOT type(r) STARTS WITH 'SIMILAR' RETURN n, r, m UNION MATCH r2 = (n)-[r]-(m) WHERE n._leid_id = m._leid_id = 186692 AND NOT type(r) STARTS WITH 'SIMILAR' RETURN n, r, m UNION MATCH r3 = (n)-[r]->(m) WHERE ID(n) = 922785 AND type(r) STARTS WITH 'SIMILAR' RETURN n, r, m

templates.name: find the Leiden community with a particular ID
templates.text: show me Leiden community with ID $id

templates.name: shows the several WCC communities
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n:Consignee)
WHERE n._wcc_id IS NOT NULL
WITH n._wcc_id AS id, count(n) AS size
ORDER BY size DESC
SKIP 1
LIMIT 14
WITH collect(id) AS ids
MATCH p=(n)--(m)
WHERE n._wcc_id IN ids
AND n._wcc_id = m._wcc_id
RETURN p

templates.name: shows all entities with name 'N/A'
templates.text: show me all entities with the name 'N/A'
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n)
WHERE n.name = 'N/A'
WITH n
OPTIONAL MATCH p=(n)--(m)
WHERE m.name = 'N/A'
RETURN n, p

templates.name: shows the similar consignees but not in the one community
templates.cypher:
MATCH p=(c1:Consignee)-[r:SIMILAR_CONSIGNEE]-(c2:Consignee)
WHERE c1._leid_id <> c2._leid_id
AND c1.shipment_count > 14
AND c2.shipment_count > 14
RETURN p
LIMIT 25

templates.name: shows what is related and how
templates.cypher:
CALL db.schema.visualization() YIELD nodes, relationships
UNWIND nodes as node
with node, relationships
WHERE apoc.node.labels(node) <> ["Bloom_Perspective"]
RETURN collect(node) AS nodes, relationships

templates.name: get random Leiden's communities
templates.cypher:
//Communities: Random Leiden
MATCH (n:Consignee)
WHERE n._leid_size > 10
WITH apoc.coll.randomItems(collect(DISTINCT n._leid_id), 25) AS ids
MATCH p=(n)--(m)
WHERE n._leid_id IN ids
AND n._leid_id = m._leid_id
RETURN p

templates.name: get random data
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n:Consignee)
WITH apoc.coll.randomItems(collect(id(n)), 10) AS ids
MATCH p = (n)-[r]-()
WHERE NOT type(r) STARTS WITH "SIMILAR"
AND id(n) IN ids
RETURN p

sceneActions.name: Get top-100 of personal community
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH p = (n)-[*..10]-(m)
WHERE id(n) in $nodes
AND n._leid_id=m._leid_id
RETURN p
LIMIT 100

sceneActions.name: Get top-100 of personal net
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH p = (n)-[*1..6]-(n)
WHERE id(n) in $nodes
AND all(x IN relationships(p) WHERE NOT type(x) CONTAINS "SIMILAR")
RETURN *
LIMIT 100

sceneActions.name: Get a chain-100 of similar
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH p = (n)-[*2..10]->(m)
WHERE id(n) in $nodes
AND all(x IN relationships(p) WHERE type(x) CONTAINS "SIMILAR")
RETURN p
LIMIT 100

sceneActions.name: Get suspicious links
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH (n)-[r]->(m)
WHERE id(n) in $nodes
AND TYPE(r) STARTS WITH "SIMILAR"
AND n._leid_id <> m._leid_id
WITH *
MATCH p = (n)--(o)--(m)
WHERE labels(o)<>labels(n)
RETURN p
LIMIT 100

sceneActions.name: Consignee: get ring
sceneActions.cypher:
MATCH (n)-[r1:CARRIES_FOR]-(Carrier)
MATCH (n)-[r2:LADING_FOR]-(PortOfLading)
MATCH (n)-[r3:SHIPS_FOR]-(Shipper)
MATCH (n)-[r4:UNLADING_FOR]-(PortOfUnlading)
MATCH (n)-[r5:NOTIFY_FOR]-(NotifyParty)
MATCH (Carrier)-[r6:CARRIES_TO]-(PortOfUnlading)
MATCH (Carrier)-[r7:CARRIES_FROM]-(PortOfLading)
MATCH (Shipper)-[r8:SHIPS_TO]-(PortOfUnlading)
MATCH (Shipper)-[r9:SHIPS_FROM]-(PortOfLading)
MATCH (Shipper)-[r10:SHIPS_BY]-(Carrier)
MATCH (NotifyParty)-[r11:NOTIFY_IN]-(PortOfUnlading)
WHERE id(n) in $nodes
RETURN *
